raw_body: ANANDAKUMAR,​ LUCIAN KUSHWANT – Beloved son of the late S. Anandakumar (Former Associate Editor,​ Sunday Observer),​ loving son of Chulani Wickramasinghe,​ brother of Yashan (Australia) and Narmada (UK),​ expired. Cremation will take place at 6 p.m. at the Kotikawatte Cemetery on Wednesday (20). Remains will be at No. 235,​ Sri Sumana Mawatha,​ Kelanimlla,​ Angoda,​ until 5.00 p.m. on Wednesday (20). 0774984594.059554
